---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About Me"
	description="I'm a pre-final year Engineering Student, Systems & Backend Developer, based in Chennai, India."
	eyebrow="Balaji"
>
	<section class="content-shell py-16"> 
		<div class="space-y-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center">
			<h1 class="m-0 text-ink text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Hi, I'm Balaji.</h1>
			<p class="m-0 text-ink text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
				I love working on backend architecture, systems programming, and building things from the ground up.
			</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-2xl">
				I'm currently a pre-final year engineering student based in Chennai, India. Most of my time goes into exploring how operating systems work, learning about memory management, and writing fast, networked backend apps. Oh, and I use Arch Linux.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="mt-8 md:mt-16 space-y-24 mb-24 px-4 sm:px-6">
		<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative border-l-2 border-[color:var(--color-border)] ml-4 pl-6 md:ml-auto md:pl-10 space-y-16">
			
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="absolute -left-[31px] md:-left-[47px] top-1.5 h-3 w-3 rounded-full border-2 border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)]"></div>
				<header class="space-y-1 mb-6">
					<p class="uppercase text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-muted m-0">Education</p>
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink m-0">SRM Valliammai Engineering College</h2>
				</header>
				<div class="space-y-1">
					<p class="text-lg font-medium text-ink m-0">B.Tech in AI and Data Science (CGPA: 8.23)</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted font-mono tracking-wide m-0 pt-1">2023 – 2027 (Expected) | Chennai, India</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="relative">
				<div class="absolute -left-[31px] md:-left-[47px] top-1.5 h-3 w-3 rounded-full border-2 border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)]"></div>
				<header class="space-y-1 mb-6">
					<p class="uppercase text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-muted m-0">Experience</p>
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink m-0">Work & Leadership</h2>
				</header>
				
				<div class="space-y-10">
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-ink m-0">Head of Marketing <span class="text-muted font-normal">— SRM VEC Campus E-Cell</span></h3>
						<span class="text-sm text-muted font-mono tracking-wide block mb-4 mt-1">Jul 2025 – Present</span>
						<ul class="text-muted list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 marker:text-border">
							<li>Ran marketing campaigns and student outreach for our campus Entrepreneurship Cell.</li>
							<li>Helped boost student engagement and event turnouts through creative promotions.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-ink m-0">Technical Leadership <span class="text-muted font-normal">— Hackathons & Events</span></h3>
						<span class="text-sm text-muted font-mono tracking-wide block mb-4 mt-1">Jul 2024 – Present</span>
						<ul class="text-muted list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 marker:text-border">
							<li>Reached the finals in 3 inter-college hackathons, mostly working on APIs and backend systems.</li>
							<li>Organized tech events on campus with over 100 participants, handling everything from logistics to the dev setups.</li>
							<li>Built and shipped an open-source project during GitHub’s <i>For the Love of Code</i> summer hackathon.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-10">
			<header class="space-y-2 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
				<p class="eyebrow m-0">My Approach</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink m-0">How I Build Things</h2>
				<p class="text-muted max-w-xl">My general approach to solving problems and writing code.</p>
			</header>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
				<div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] p-8 hover:border-muted transition-colors">
					<Icon name="lucide:layers" class="w-6 h-6 text-muted mb-5" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Systems Thinking</h3>
					<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed m-0 text-sm">I like my code to be predictable and easy to maintain. I usually start with figuring out the data structures and APIs first, making sure the foundation makes sense before piling features on top.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] p-8 hover:border-muted transition-colors">
					<Icon name="lucide:book-open" class="w-6 h-6 text-muted mb-5" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Deep Dives</h3>
					<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed m-0 text-sm">I don't just use tools; I like to learn how they actually work under the hood.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] p-8 hover:border-muted transition-colors">
					<Icon name="lucide:zap" class="w-6 h-6 text-muted mb-5" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Performance First</h3>
					<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed m-0 text-sm">Writing efficient, lightweight, and fast code is always on my mind.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="md:col-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] p-8 hover:border-muted transition-colors">
					<Icon name="lucide:refresh-cw" class="w-6 h-6 text-muted mb-5" />
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Curiosity Driven</h3>
					<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed m-0 text-sm">Tech moves fast, so I'm always picking up new things. Whether it's messing around with a new language or trying out a different system design pattern, I enjoy the learning process.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-10">
			<header class="space-y-2 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
				<p class="eyebrow m-0">Technical Skills</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink m-0">My Stack</h2>
				<p class="text-muted max-w-xl">The languages and tools I reach for most often.</p>
			</header>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:go" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Go</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:python" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Python</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:openjdk" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Java</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:postgresql" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">PostgreSQL</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:docker" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Docker</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:linux" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">Linux</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:fastapi" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">FastAPI</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-surface)] hover:border-muted hover:bg-[color:color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-border)_20%,transparent)] transition-all">
					<Icon name="simple-icons:mongodb" class="w-10 h-10 text-muted mb-3" />
					<span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink">MongoDB</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
